      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the usual wear you\u2019d expect from an older used car, but it\u2019s priced to make sense and has a lot to offer for the money. If you\u2019re after something honest, affordable, and ready to be put to use, this could be a great fit.",
