    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget project or daily-with-character. This car shows cosmetic wear and age, but it still offers a willing powertrain, responsive chassis feel, and the kind of analog driving experience that\u2019s getting harder to find. Engine starts, runs, and pulls with good urgency, transmission engages as it should, and the car tracks down the road with a planted feel. A great candidate for someone who wants usable transportation now and a platform to sort and improve over time. If you know how to wrench, there\u2019s real value here.",
